616
00:30:55,000 --> 00:30:57,040
A person who worships the golden calf like you.

617
00:30:57,040 --> 00:30:58,000
How can I trust you?

618
00:30:58,560 --> 00:30:59,680
Why do you talk so much?

619
00:30:59,680 --> 00:31:00,760
Do you dare to bet or not?

620
00:31:04,160 --> 00:31:05,479
Sure. Why not?!

621
00:31:05,479 --> 00:31:07,479
If Sun Bufan can be executed,

