664
00:33:07,040 --> 00:33:09,439
Whatever. I'm not afraid.

665
00:33:13,280 --> 00:33:15,760
You know you will lose, but you still wanna bet.

666
00:33:18,920 --> 00:33:20,079
Is this a trap?

667
00:33:27,359 --> 00:33:29,560
You won't come back anymore.

668
00:33:31,199 --> 00:33:32,319
